00:14:02,974 --> 00:14:05,101
Mabilis na gumalaw. Magsisimula na ang laro.

247
00:14:05,309 --> 00:14:06,869
Gawin natin sa labas, mas mabilis.

248
00:14:07,937 --> 00:14:09,272
<i>Ano ang nangyayari?</i>

249
00:14:10,314 --> 00:14:11,858
<i>Bakit biglang umikot ang tubig?</i>

250
00:14:14,193 --> 00:14:16,278
- Nakakabaliw, bro. Magaling siya.
- Oo kuya.

251
00:14:16,279 --> 00:14:18,156
Alam mo, inaamin ko
hindi magagawa iyon. Kahanga-hanga.

252
00:14:29,167 --> 00:14:30,167
<i>Iyon lang?</i>

253
00:14:30,751 --> 00:14:31,919
<i>Hindi niya ako ibubully?</i>

254
00:14:33,171 --> 00:14:34,589
<i>Ano ang nangyayari?</i>

255
00:14:35,381 --> 00:14:37,758
<i>Bakit bigla silang tumigil sa pag-aalaga?</i>

256
00:14:43,764 --> 00:14:46,100
Hello! Ci-N! Ako ito!

257
00:14:46,392 --> 00:14:47,392
<i>At sino ka?</i>

258
00:14:47,602 --> 00:14:50,562
Si Jay-jay naman! Anong nangyare sayo?
Bakit ka lumalaktaw sa klase?

259
00:14:50,563 --> 00:14:52,940
<i>Ipagpaumanhin mo. Pwede bang pakiusap
hindi sumisigaw sa telepono?</i>

260
00:14:53,274 --> 00:14:56,026
pasensya na po. Anong nangyari sayo?

261
00:14:56,027 --> 00:14:57,611
<i>Hindi maganda ang pakiramdam ko.</i>

262
00:14:57,612 --> 00:14:59,988
- Huh?
<i>- Bakit? Miss na miss mo na ba ako?</i>

263
00:14:59,989 --> 00:15:01,699
Hindi, baliw ka ba?

264
00:15:01,908 --> 00:15:03,116
<i>Oh, talaga?</i>

265
00:15:03,117 --> 00:15:04,159
<i>Sige. Bye.</i>

266
00:15:04,160 --> 00:15:07,538
Teka! Gusto ko lang malaman kung okay ka lang.

267
00:15:07,914 --> 00:15:09,373
Kailan ka babalik sa paaralan?

268
00:15:09,624 --> 00:15:11,375
<i>So inaamin mo na na-miss mo ako?</i>

269
00:15:11,751 --> 00:15:13,461
<i>Balik ako sa paaralan sa susunod na linggo.</i>

270
00:15:13,878 --> 00:15:16,464
ha? Anong nangyari sayo?

271
00:15:17,298 --> 00:15:18,298
<i>Wala.</i>

272
00:15:18,508 --> 00:15:20,551
<i>Masama lang ang pakiramdam ko.</i>

273
00:15:20,635 --> 00:15:21,719
<i>Bakit mo itinulak ito?</i>

274
00:15:21,802 --> 00:15:24,262
Ano ang ibig mong sabihin
"hindi maganda ang pakiramdam?"

275
00:15:24,263 --> 00:15:26,891
Ang susunod na linggo ay masyadong mahaba. Ano ang iyong sakit?

276
00:15:27,183 --> 00:15:28,851
<i>Masakit ang ingrown ko.</i>

277
00:15:29,018 --> 00:15:31,646
Walang pag-asa ang pakikipag-usap sa iyo,
Ci-N! Nakakainis!

278
00:15:32,313 --> 00:15:33,497
<i>Magkikita na lang tayo
kapag nakikita kita, Jay.</i>

279
00:15:33,522 --> 00:15:36,108
Teka, si Keifer kasi eh
at ang iba ay...

280
00:15:46,369 --> 00:15:47,036
Ay, Aries!

281
00:15:47,370 --> 00:15:48,370
ano?

282
00:15:48,871 --> 00:15:49,871
Umm...

283
00:15:51,290 --> 00:15:52,290
ano?

284
00:15:53,334 --> 00:15:55,044
May ginawa ka ba laban sa Section E?

285
00:15:56,504 --> 00:15:58,673
Ako? Gumawa ng isang bagay laban sa Seksyon E?

286
00:15:59,048 --> 00:16:00,048
Seryoso ka ba?

287
00:16:00,800 --> 00:16:02,426
Saka bakit hindi nila ako kinakausap?

288
00:16:02,802 --> 00:16:06,347
Hindi ako ang magtatanong
bakit may mga bulok na mansanas diyan.

289
00:16:07,765 --> 00:16:08,933
Ito ay dahil...

290
00:16:10,184 --> 00:16:13,896
iba na ang pakikitungo nila sa akin
nung nalaman nila na isa akong Fernandez.

291
00:16:14,605 --> 00:16:15,398
hindi ko alam.

292
00:16:15,398 --> 00:16:16,357
Siguro dahil kay Angelo.

293
00:16:16,358 --> 00:16:17,733
Fernandez din siya.

294
00:16:19,527 --> 00:16:21,319
Ngunit ikaw ang isa
tinanong nila ako.

295
00:16:21,320 --> 00:16:23,531
Kung ikaw at ako ay magkamag-anak.

296
00:16:23,864 --> 00:16:25,324
Jay-jay, wala akong ideya.

297
00:16:25,741 --> 00:16:28,201
Bakit hindi mo sila tanungin ng diretso
ano problema nila sayo?

298
00:16:28,202 --> 00:16:29,203
Huwag mo akong pakialaman.

299
00:16:40,423 --> 00:16:43,342
Guys, nakuha ko yung school records niya.

300
00:16:43,718 --> 00:16:45,261
Ang una ay mula sa punong-guro.

301
00:16:45,761 --> 00:16:47,597
Ang isa ay mula sa dati niyang paaralan.

302
00:16:48,222 --> 00:16:51,726
Walang gaanong impormasyon tungkol sa kanya
mula sa HVIS noong huli...

303
00:16:52,059 --> 00:16:53,819
dahil siya lang
nagsimula dito, siyempre.

304
00:16:54,312 --> 00:16:57,315
Pero kung susuriin mo siya
mga nakaraang rekord ng paaralan...

305
00:16:58,441 --> 00:16:59,441
Damn!

306
00:17:01,068 --> 00:17:02,570
Sinaksak ng lapis ang kaklase?

307
00:17:02,945 --> 00:17:03,945
Seryoso?

308
00:17:04,280 --> 00:17:05,364
Sinuntok ng ibang estudyante?

309
00:17:07,325 --> 00:17:08,325
Wow.

310
00:17:08,367 --> 00:17:10,202
Tamang-tama siya sa Section E.

311
00:17:11,329 --> 00:17:12,622
So far, yun lang ang nakita ko.

312
00:17:12,830 --> 00:17:14,070
Suriin kung may iba pa.

313
00:17:15,625 --> 00:17:19,253
Guys, guys. Hulaan nyo?

314
00:17:20,254 --> 00:17:23,466
Nalaman ko na sila Aries at Jay-jay
ang mga ina ay kapatid sa ama.

315
00:17:24,133 --> 00:17:25,384
May broken family sila.

316
00:17:25,843 --> 00:17:27,428
Ang kanyang ama ay wala kahit saan.

317
00:17:27,720 --> 00:17:29,847
At ang kanyang ina ay naging
nagpakasal ng maraming beses.

318
00:17:30,056 --> 00:17:31,376
Lumaki siya kasama ang kanyang lola.

319
00:17:31,807 --> 00:17:33,434
Ngunit ito ang pinakamahalagang bahagi.

320
00:17:33,726 --> 00:17:37,313
Kamakailan lamang, siya ay naging
kinuha ng ina ni Aries.

321
00:17:38,481 --> 00:17:41,108
Kaya posible na siya
pag-espiya sa amin para kay Aries.

322
00:17:41,943 --> 00:17:43,194
Bro, ano ba.

323
00:17:43,611 --> 00:17:44,611
Posible.

324
00:17:44,654 --> 00:17:49,158
Sa palagay mo ba ito ay ang kanyang ideya na
nilagay yung pinsan niyang manggugulo sa section namin?

325
00:18:00,753 --> 00:18:05,675
Okay, lahat. Sa aming susunod na sesyon,
mag-a-apply kami ng mga lecture.

326
00:18:06,175 --> 00:18:07,175
Oo ma'am.

327
00:18:07,176 --> 00:18:08,010
Okay, ma'am.

328
00:18:08,011 --> 00:18:10,179
Isang linggo na nila akong hindi pinapansin.

329
00:18:10,781 --> 00:18:13,407
<i>- Siguro kung ano ang pinaplano ng mga asshole na ito para sa akin?</i>
- Oo nga pala, klase.

330
00:18:13,432 --> 00:18:15,476
Huwag kalimutang maglinis bago pumunta.

331
00:18:15,768 --> 00:18:17,812
Pinakiusapan ako ni Sir Alvin
paalalahanan ka. O kung hindi...

332
00:18:18,604 --> 00:18:20,231
Kaya linisin mo itong kwarto.

333
00:18:21,065 --> 00:18:22,108
See you bukas.

334
00:18:22,483 --> 00:18:24,402
- Okay, ma'am.
- See you.

335
00:18:29,365 --> 00:18:31,534
Uuwi na ako ngayon.

336
00:18:33,911 --> 00:18:35,955
- Saan tayo pupunta ngayong gabi?
- Hapunan?

337
00:18:37,248 --> 00:18:39,041
Parang walang nagbabalak maglinis.

338
00:18:39,333 --> 00:18:40,543
Lalabas na lahat.

339
00:18:42,586 --> 00:18:44,295
Hey. Sinabihan kaming maglinis.

340
00:18:44,296 --> 00:18:45,672
Inaasahan mo bang gagawin ko ulit mag-isa?

341
00:18:45,673 --> 00:18:46,673
Anong nangyare sayo?!

342
00:18:48,384 --> 00:18:49,426
Sige, ikulong mo siya.

343
00:18:49,427 --> 00:18:52,138
<i>[nagtatawanan ang mga mag-aaral]</i>

344
00:18:52,471 --> 00:18:55,808
Kung pipilitin mo akong linisin,
hindi mo man lang ako papansinin!

345
00:18:55,850 --> 00:18:58,310
Maglinis ka na lang para makaalis ka na.

346
00:19:00,688 --> 00:19:03,107
Bini-bully ako
tuktok ng hindi pinapansin.

347
00:19:07,611 --> 00:19:09,739
So, anong gagawin natin kay Jay-jay?

348
00:19:10,281 --> 00:19:11,490
Kailangan natin siyang paalisin.

349
00:19:12,742 --> 00:19:13,742
Pero paano?

350
00:19:14,326 --> 00:19:16,704
Ang iyong "pagpanggap na wala siya"
parang hindi gumana ang plano.

351
00:19:17,288 --> 00:19:19,874
She's such a badass.
Hindi ka tugma sa kanya.

352
00:19:20,082 --> 00:19:21,333
Walang paraan!

353
00:19:22,334 --> 00:19:25,463
Kailangan lang nating gawing miserable ang buhay niya
hanggang sa napagdesisyunan niyang umalis mag-isa.

354
00:19:29,759 --> 00:19:32,970
Oh, talaga? Pagkatapos ay maghihintay sila nang walang kabuluhan.

355
00:19:34,472 --> 00:19:36,348
Akala ba nila madali nila akong matatanggal?

356
00:19:36,640 --> 00:19:37,640
Bantayan mo ako.

357
00:19:39,685 --> 00:19:41,145
Puno ng sarili nila.

358
00:19:43,939 --> 00:19:44,939
Oops.

359
00:19:46,192 --> 00:19:47,193
Madumi pa rin dito.

360
00:19:49,195 --> 00:19:50,946
Nakalimutan mo ang basura.

361
00:19:52,490 --> 00:19:53,783
Nakakatawa ba iyon sa iyo?

362
00:19:54,241 --> 00:19:55,034
Nalilibang ka ba?

363
00:19:55,242 --> 00:19:55,826
Oo.

364
00:19:56,202 --> 00:19:57,202
Nakakatuwa naman.

365
00:20:00,372 --> 00:20:01,373
Linisin ito.

366
00:20:10,007 --> 00:20:11,258
Sa tingin mo ba cool ka?

367
00:20:12,510 --> 00:20:13,886
Ito ba ang gusto mo?

368
00:20:14,762 --> 00:20:17,889
Halika na!

369
00:20:17,890 --> 00:20:22,769
Ayan! Basura! Linisin mo yan!

370
00:20:22,770 --> 00:20:23,938
Itigil mo na!

371
00:20:24,104 --> 00:20:25,563
Siya lang ang nakakagawa ng eksena?

372
00:20:25,564 --> 00:20:27,608
tumatanggi ako! Maglinis kayong lahat!

373
00:20:28,108 --> 00:20:29,108
Sige.

374
00:20:30,069 --> 00:20:31,403
Maglilinis din tayo.

375
00:20:31,529 --> 00:20:32,529
Teka...

376
00:20:32,655 --> 00:20:34,090
Bakit tayo kinakaladkad dito?

377
00:20:34,114 --> 00:20:35,574
Hindi kami kasali sa gulo na yan.

378
00:20:35,699 --> 00:20:37,909
Ako ang presidente ng klase.
Hindi ako naglilinis.

379
00:20:37,910 --> 00:20:39,953
At paano kung ikaw ang presidente ng klase?

380
00:20:39,954 --> 00:20:42,580
Hindi iyon exempt sa iyo sa paglilinis!

381
00:20:42,581 --> 00:20:43,123
Ano ang f...

382
00:20:43,124 --> 00:20:45,291
Isang class president yan
exempted sa paglilinis?

383
00:20:45,292 --> 00:20:46,876
Wow. Diktador masyado?

384
00:20:46,877 --> 00:20:48,586
Ikaw ang gumawa
ang gulo na ito in the first place!

385
00:20:48,587 --> 00:20:50,713
Oo, ginawa ko itong gulo! Kaya ano?

386
00:20:50,714 --> 00:20:52,216
Gusto mo pa?

387
00:20:52,675 --> 00:20:53,884
Eto na!

388
00:20:54,385 --> 00:20:57,012
Sige. Gumawa ng gulo. Sige na.

389
00:20:57,137 --> 00:20:59,138
Sa tingin mo hindi ako tatayo sayo?

390
00:20:59,139 --> 00:21:00,306
Sa iyong mukha, Mr. Class President.

391
00:21:00,823 --> 00:21:03,726
Sige, gumawa ka ng gulo! Gawin mo!

392
00:21:03,727 --> 00:21:05,139
Sa tingin mo natatakot ako sayo?

393
00:21:06,021 --> 00:21:07,022
Maglinis ka na lang din.

394
00:21:07,064 --> 00:21:08,064
Bakit?

395
00:21:11,610 --> 00:21:13,570
Hindi pa namin alam kung ano
may pakana ang babaeng iyon.

396
00:21:13,571 --> 00:21:16,657
Baka pinapunta siya ni Aries para guluhin kami.

397
00:21:20,244 --> 00:21:21,745
Babalik si David, di ba?

398
00:21:35,259 --> 00:21:36,385
Simulan ang paglilinis!

399
00:21:46,145 --> 00:21:47,229
Napakasaya, hindi ba?

400
00:21:51,901 --> 00:21:52,901
Masaya?

401
00:21:53,193 --> 00:21:56,071
Hindi ko sasabihin nang eksakto ang pagiging
Ang nakakulong dito kasama ka ay masaya.

402
00:21:56,614 --> 00:21:58,198
Ngunit hindi ba ito ang iyong kasalanan?

403
00:21:59,533 --> 00:22:00,533
kasalanan ko?

404
00:22:01,285 --> 00:22:03,370
Ikaw ang nagtapon ng basura sa akin.

405
00:22:03,746 --> 00:22:04,413
At bakit?

406
00:22:04,747 --> 00:22:05,747
Sino ang unang gumawa nito?

407
00:22:05,915 --> 00:22:07,791
Ikaw iyon, Mr. Class President.

408
00:22:17,885 --> 00:22:19,345
Sino ba si David?

409
00:22:25,476 --> 00:22:26,518
Si David ay...

410
00:22:28,854 --> 00:22:30,689
ang orihinal na pangulo ng klase.

411
00:22:31,982 --> 00:22:33,734
Ah, orihinal.

412
00:22:34,193 --> 00:22:36,153
So, ninakaw mo sa kanya ang posisyon na iyon?

413
00:22:41,033 --> 00:22:42,033
may tanong ako.

414
00:22:45,788 --> 00:22:46,788
Ano na ngayon?

415
00:22:48,207 --> 00:22:51,043
Bakit mo ako iniiwasan noong natuto ka
na pinsan ko si Aries?

416
00:23:09,728 --> 00:23:10,980
Aries, ihinto mo ang sasakyan!!!

417
00:23:11,146 --> 00:23:11,730
ano?

418
00:23:11,939 --> 00:23:12,982
Si Ci-N ba yun?

419
00:23:13,399 --> 00:23:14,441
Siya ito.

420
00:23:14,525 --> 00:23:15,818
Aalis na ako dito.

421
00:23:16,318 --> 00:23:19,028
Siguraduhin mo Angelo
Alam kong hinatid kita sa paaralan.

422
00:23:19,029 --> 00:23:19,905
Syempre!

423
00:23:19,905 --> 00:23:20,905
Ci-N!

424
00:23:21,532 --> 00:23:22,532
Ci-N!

425
00:23:24,410 --> 00:23:25,828
Anong balak mo?

426
00:23:26,662 --> 00:23:28,622
- Buti na lang babalik ka na sa school!
- Aray.

427
00:23:29,540 --> 00:23:30,541
Mag-ingat ka!

428
00:23:33,043 --> 00:23:34,628
Parang sira ka.

429
00:23:35,462 --> 00:23:37,089
Ang dami mong sugat at pasa.

430
00:23:37,464 --> 00:23:38,465
Ito ay wala.

431
00:23:38,757 --> 00:23:39,757
Napasubsob ako sa mukha ko.

432
00:23:40,009 --> 00:23:42,803
Nahulog? Ano ang ginawa ng pavement, sinuntok ka?

433
00:23:44,096 --> 00:23:45,096
Dito.

434
00:23:45,264 --> 00:23:47,306
Lagi ko itong nasa bag ko. Gamitin ito.

435
00:23:47,307 --> 00:23:49,351
Hindi na kailangan iyon.

436
00:23:49,893 --> 00:23:50,894
Jay-jay, wala ito.

437
00:23:51,186 --> 00:23:52,604
Masyado kang nag-aalala.

438
00:23:53,063 --> 00:23:54,064
Overacting ka.

439
00:23:54,898 --> 00:23:55,898
Tapos wag na.

440
00:23:58,277 --> 00:23:59,528
Siya nga pala, Ci-N.

441
00:24:00,154 --> 00:24:01,864
May nangyari sa Section E.

442
00:24:02,239 --> 00:24:03,824
Hindi yan balita sa akin.

443
00:24:04,366 --> 00:24:05,868
Hindi. Iba ito.

444
00:24:06,744 --> 00:24:07,995
Si Keifer ito...

445
00:24:08,871 --> 00:24:09,871
anong nangyari?

446
00:24:11,290 --> 00:24:12,708
Ako ay isang Fernandez.

447
00:24:13,625 --> 00:24:16,045
Jasper Jean Fernandez Mariano.

448
00:24:17,296 --> 00:24:18,672
Magpinsan kami ni Aries.

449
00:24:19,214 --> 00:24:20,214
Kaya narinig ko.

450
00:24:21,735 --> 00:24:23,485
Tapos ikaw ba...

451
00:24:23,510 --> 00:24:25,012
iwasan mo rin ako ngayon?

452
00:24:30,768 --> 00:24:31,769
Syempre hindi.

453
00:24:32,686 --> 00:24:33,729
Bakit ko naman gagawin yun?

454
00:24:35,522 --> 00:24:36,690
Salamat, Ci-N.

455
00:24:37,941 --> 00:24:40,652
Pero paano kung makita ng iba
na kinakausap mo ako?

456
00:24:41,195 --> 00:24:43,739
Sasabihin ko na lang sa kanila na hindi ako
Alam kong isa kang Fernandez.

457
00:24:43,906 --> 00:24:44,531
Madali.

458
00:24:44,532 --> 00:24:47,785
- Napakagaling mo.
- Oo naman.

459
00:24:48,035 --> 00:24:49,161
Ikaw ang idol ko.

460
00:24:50,370 --> 00:24:54,707
<i>[nagsisigawan ang mga estudyante]</i>

461
00:24:54,708 --> 00:24:56,085
Anong nangyayari dito?

462
00:24:57,961 --> 00:24:59,922
Oo! Suntukin mo siya sa mukha!

463
00:25:00,798 --> 00:25:03,550
Hindi ko siya nakilala.
Si David lang pala.

464
00:25:07,513 --> 00:25:08,847
Bakit may babae dito?

465
00:25:09,014 --> 00:25:10,848
Sige na! Lumaban ka!

466
00:25:10,849 --> 00:25:14,268
<i>[patuloy na pagpalakpak]</i>

467
00:25:14,269 --> 00:25:15,269
Alam mo, sa tingin ko tayo
mabuti pang umalis ka na dito.

468
00:25:15,270 --> 00:25:16,270
Puno ka pa ng sugat.

469
00:25:16,271 --> 00:25:19,024
- Umalis ka dito.
- Teka, tapusin muna natin itong panoorin.

470
00:25:19,358 --> 00:25:22,736
Hindi ba dapat umiwas tayo?
O hindi bababa sa pigilan sila?

471
00:25:22,986 --> 00:25:24,822
Hindi pa rin sila nakikinig sa amin.

472
00:25:25,114 --> 00:25:25,948
Gusto mong subukan?

473
00:25:26,073 --> 00:25:26,865
Pumunta at pigilan sila.

474
00:25:26,949 --> 00:25:27,949
Labanan!!!

475
00:25:29,159 --> 00:25:30,159
suntukin mo siya!

476
00:25:31,495 --> 00:25:33,288
Please tigilan mo na to?!

477
00:25:34,289 --> 00:25:35,457
- Aray!
- Ano ang impiyerno?

478
00:25:36,125 --> 00:25:37,417
Walang tigil!

479
00:25:55,310 --> 00:25:56,310
ano ba naman

480
00:26:00,899 --> 00:26:01,899
Tinapon mo ba yan?

481
00:26:01,942 --> 00:26:02,942
Oo, ginawa niya!

482
00:26:03,777 --> 00:26:04,777
Huwag kang makialam!

483
00:26:05,058 --> 00:26:07,632
Kung nasaktan ako, kunin mo ba ako
sa ospital, ha?

484
00:26:07,858 --> 00:26:09,401
Hindi ba ako ang kalaban mo?

485
00:26:09,491 --> 00:26:10,784
Itigil mo na!

486
00:26:13,537 --> 00:26:14,830
Re-election tayo.

487
00:26:15,122 --> 00:26:17,541
Kung saan mas organisado
at walang manloloko.

488
00:26:17,749 --> 00:26:18,876
Kung sino man ang manalo...

489
00:26:19,001 --> 00:26:20,627
magiging class president.

490
00:26:21,295 --> 00:26:22,421
Patas at parisukat.

491
00:26:23,130 --> 00:26:24,423
Game ako niyan.

492
00:26:25,424 --> 00:26:28,135
Hangga't walang gagawin
magtapon ng mga upuan, o basura.

493
00:26:28,760 --> 00:26:29,386
Laro.

494
00:26:29,595 --> 00:26:31,930
At bakit ako magtapon ng mga bagay
sa panahon ng eleksyon sa klase?

495
00:26:33,056 --> 00:26:35,475
Sige. Mamaya, pagkatapos ng klase.

496
00:26:36,310 --> 00:26:38,604
Ayusin natin ang kwarto
bago makarating dito si Sir Alvin.

497
00:26:40,314 --> 00:26:42,232
Paano pilay. Nagiging exciting na.

498
00:26:42,733 --> 00:26:44,526
Sayang ang pera.

499
00:26:48,238 --> 00:26:49,573
Hey, Ci-N.

500
00:26:50,324 --> 00:26:52,618
Anong meron sa re-election na yan?

501
00:26:52,951 --> 00:26:53,951
Maghintay ka lang.

502
00:26:54,286 --> 00:26:55,745
Mas maganda kapag surprise.

503
00:26:55,746 --> 00:26:57,372
Sabihin mo lang.

504
00:26:57,998 --> 00:26:58,665
ayos lang.

505
00:26:58,916 --> 00:26:59,916
Kaya lang...

506
00:27:00,125 --> 00:27:01,125
isang patas na laban.

507
00:27:01,543 --> 00:27:02,836
Tingnan mo na lang mamaya.

508
00:27:03,545 --> 00:27:05,464
Ang tanging bagay na kailangan mong malaman...

509
00:27:05,756 --> 00:27:07,758
Si David ang orihinal na pangulo.

510
00:27:08,300 --> 00:27:09,510
Abangan mo na lang mamaya, okay?

511
00:27:09,718 --> 00:27:11,261
Kawawang David.

512
00:27:12,512 --> 00:27:14,056
Oh! Oo nga pala...

513
00:27:15,140 --> 00:27:16,974
Paano ka napunta sa Section E?

514
00:27:16,975 --> 00:27:19,061
Sana this time ikaw
kayang sagutin ito ng tapat.

515
00:27:21,647 --> 00:27:23,732
Nagkaroon din ako ng suntukan noon.

516
00:27:24,358 --> 00:27:25,734
Medyo kumplikado.

517
00:27:26,568 --> 00:27:28,487
May konting halik din sa timpla.

518
00:27:30,697 --> 00:27:32,823
Hindi ka ba masyadong bata para makipaghalikan kahit kanino?

519
00:27:32,824 --> 00:27:34,493
Umasta ka na para kang matandang babae.

520
00:27:35,118 --> 00:27:36,703
Kaya, paano ito aktwal na nangyari?

521
00:27:37,204 --> 00:27:38,497
Ikaw ba ang gumawa ng first move?

522
00:27:40,123 --> 00:27:41,250
May ganyan.

523
00:27:42,960 --> 00:27:43,627
Masakit, Jay.

524
00:27:43,628 --> 00:27:45,671
Ang tanga mo anak.

525
00:27:46,922 --> 00:27:47,922
Ikwento.

526
00:27:48,382 --> 00:27:49,216
- Paano mo hinalikan?
- Hindi.

527
00:27:49,216 --> 00:27:49,841
ayoko.

528
00:27:49,842 --> 00:27:53,136
- Halika, ibuhos ito!
- Masyado kang mapilit, Jay!

529
00:27:53,303 --> 00:27:57,432
Jasper Jean Mariano,
ikaw at ang buong Seksyon E ay pinagbawalan...

530
00:27:58,100 --> 00:28:01,394
mula sa pagpasok sa HVIS Cafeteria
sa utos ng student council.

531
00:28:01,395 --> 00:28:02,395
Seryoso?

532
00:28:02,638 --> 00:28:03,998
Pinagbawalan din ako sa canteen?

533
00:28:04,356 --> 00:28:05,399
Anong klaseng biro ito?

534
00:28:08,277 --> 00:28:09,637
Galing ka sa Section E, di ba?

535
00:28:10,028 --> 00:28:11,405
Paano tayo kukuha ng pagkain ngayon?

536
00:28:13,490 --> 00:28:14,490
tama ka.

537
00:28:15,450 --> 00:28:18,161
Nakakainis! Ang mga uod sa
kumakalam ang tummy ko ngayon.

538
00:28:19,496 --> 00:28:21,915
Magdadala na lang ako ng sarili kong pagkain simula ngayon.

539
00:28:22,499 --> 00:28:23,979
Bakit hindi ka rin magdala ng para sa akin?

540
00:28:24,334 --> 00:28:25,376
Hindi mo ba masyadong pinipilit ang swerte mo?

541
00:28:25,377 --> 00:28:26,461
Halika na.

542
00:28:26,753 --> 00:28:27,921
Busy ang lahat sa bahay.

543
00:28:29,256 --> 00:28:29,923
Pakiusap...

544
00:28:29,924 --> 00:28:31,717
I'll share my food with you then.

545
00:28:32,175 --> 00:28:33,175
Oo!

546
00:28:35,971 --> 00:28:36,971
Hi, Rakki!

547
00:28:39,558 --> 00:28:40,599
Kayo mga babae sige.

548
00:28:40,600 --> 00:28:42,185
paalam. See you later.

549
00:28:42,436 --> 00:28:43,436
Jay-jay, kamusta?

550
00:28:43,937 --> 00:28:44,937
Okay ka lang?

551
00:28:45,564 --> 00:28:46,523
Kaya lang...

552
00:28:46,524 --> 00:28:48,108
nagugutom na ako. Ikaw?

553
00:28:48,817 --> 00:28:49,817
Paano naman ako?

554
00:28:50,610 --> 00:28:51,796
Hindi mo ba tatanungin kung kumusta ako?

555
00:28:51,820 --> 00:28:54,197
Hindi na kailangan. halata naman
nag away kayo.

556
00:28:55,866 --> 00:28:56,866
Dummy.

557
00:28:57,075 --> 00:28:58,577
Bakit, wala ka bang kinakain?

558
00:28:58,994 --> 00:29:01,204
hindi pa. Banned din ako sa canteen.

559
00:29:01,413 --> 00:29:02,413
Ganoon ba?

560
00:29:02,622 --> 00:29:03,332
Paano ito?

561
00:29:03,623 --> 00:29:04,750
Bigyan mo lang ako ng pera mo.

562
00:29:04,875 --> 00:29:06,543
Tingnan ko kung ano ang magagawa ko.

563
00:29:07,461 --> 00:29:08,837
- Sigurado ka ba?
- Oo.

564
00:29:09,963 --> 00:29:10,963
Ibigay mo, dali.

565
00:29:13,342 --> 00:29:15,802
Kukuha ako ng kanin at menudo. Ikaw, Ci-N?

566
00:29:16,553 --> 00:29:17,763
Kukuha ako ng special order.

567
00:29:18,388 --> 00:29:19,598
Ito ay tinatawag na "Rakki."

568
00:29:19,806 --> 00:29:21,558
talaga. Ano ang iyong order?

569
00:29:22,184 --> 00:29:23,685
Magkakaroon ako ng katulad ni Jay-jay.

570
00:29:24,019 --> 00:29:26,271
- Okay. mauuna na ako.
- Salamat, Rakki.

571
00:29:32,861 --> 00:29:34,529
Hoy... anong nangyare sa inyong dalawa?

572
00:29:35,322 --> 00:29:36,322
wala.

573
00:29:36,782 --> 00:29:37,782
wala yun.

574
00:29:39,826 --> 00:29:44,998
Ahhhh, so the kiss you
were telling me about is with...

575
00:29:46,875 --> 00:29:48,125
Kasama si Rakki?

576
00:29:48,126 --> 00:29:49,126
Oo.

577
00:29:49,419 --> 00:29:51,755
Wow. Hindi ko inaasahan yun.
Hinalikan mo talaga?

578
00:29:52,923 --> 00:29:53,924
Hinalikan ko siya.

579
00:29:54,424 --> 00:29:55,424
Paano?

580
00:29:56,510 --> 00:29:57,219
Nangyari lang.

581
00:29:57,427 --> 00:29:59,554
Naglapit ang mukha namin tapos...

582
00:30:00,472 --> 00:30:01,723
Hinalikan ko siya.

583
00:30:02,849 --> 00:30:04,101
She punched me after, though.

584
00:30:04,976 --> 00:30:06,478
Palihim ka talaga.

585
00:30:12,526 --> 00:30:13,901
Ang ganda ni Rakki noh?

586
00:30:13,902 --> 00:30:16,530
Kailangan naming kumain dahil sa kanya,
ngayon naiintindihan ko na kung bakit mo siya nagustuhan.

587
00:30:16,822 --> 00:30:17,906
Sabihin mo sa akin ang tungkol dito.

588
00:30:18,407 --> 00:30:22,035
Teka, bakit tayo nandito?
Hindi ba tayo patungo sa muling halalan?

589
00:30:23,745 --> 00:30:25,621
Halika, ilagay ang iyong malaking taya dito mismo!

590
00:30:25,622 --> 00:30:27,249
Tataya ako kay Keifer!

591
00:30:27,749 --> 00:30:30,585
Keifer! Keifer! Keifer!

592
00:30:38,760 --> 00:30:41,012
Sige guys. Makinig ka!

593
00:30:43,265 --> 00:30:47,060
Oras na para sa muling halalan!

594
00:30:50,647 --> 00:30:52,983
Sobrang saya, see?
May announcer pa kami.

595
00:30:53,525 --> 00:30:55,443
- Ang iyong muling halalan ay ganito?
- Tayo na, Keifer!

596
00:30:55,444 --> 00:30:56,944
Seryoso ka?!

597
00:30:56,945 --> 00:30:58,029
Simple lang ang mga patakaran...

598
00:30:59,156 --> 00:31:00,532
Laban hanggang dulo.

599
00:31:00,991 --> 00:31:03,701
David laban kay Keifer.

600
00:31:03,702 --> 00:31:05,537
Huling nakatayo...

601
00:31:05,620 --> 00:31:07,079
dapat maging presidente!

602
00:31:07,080 --> 00:31:10,958
[nagpapalakpak]

603
00:31:10,959 --> 00:31:14,503
Keifer!

604
00:31:14,504 --> 00:31:16,839
- David! David! David!
- Keifer, alis na tayo!

605
00:31:16,840 --> 00:31:17,466
Keifer, tara na!

606
00:31:17,467 --> 00:31:21,594
Talunin mo siya, David!
Siya ay walang iba kundi isang magandang mukha!

607
00:31:21,595 --> 00:31:24,221
Kaya mo yan, David, go!

608
00:31:24,222 --> 00:31:25,931
David!

609
00:31:25,932 --> 00:31:28,101
Sige sige mag-stretch ka.

610
00:31:29,686 --> 00:31:30,686
ano?

611
00:31:30,687 --> 00:31:32,980
Kailangan mong manalo, pare.
Malaki ang taya ko sa iyo.

612
00:31:32,981 --> 00:31:35,734
- David, kailangan mong manalo!
- Tayo na!

613
00:31:37,027 --> 00:31:38,487
David!

614
00:31:39,863 --> 00:31:42,866
Keifer!

615
00:31:44,284 --> 00:31:46,244
- Halika, Keifer!
- sabi ko David!

616
00:31:48,246 --> 00:31:50,415
Sige na, David!

617
00:31:54,419 --> 00:31:56,213
Okay, guys, bago kayo magsimula...

618
00:31:56,505 --> 00:31:57,756
mag fist bump tayo.

619
00:31:59,466 --> 00:32:00,466
Okay.

620
00:32:00,967 --> 00:32:03,303
Humanda tayo sa pagdagundong!

621
00:32:11,102 --> 00:32:12,187
Tara na, Keifer!

622
00:32:14,940 --> 00:32:15,940
Sige, suntukin mo siya!

623
00:32:16,816 --> 00:32:18,109
Bigyan mo siya ng isa pa!

624
00:32:20,779 --> 00:32:21,779
David?

625
00:32:24,032 --> 00:32:24,783
Madali!

626
00:32:24,784 --> 00:32:25,784
Tara na!

627
00:32:32,624 --> 00:32:34,918
Halika, lalaki! Malaki ang taya ko dito.

628
00:32:38,547 --> 00:32:39,798
Halika, David!

629
00:32:41,466 --> 00:32:42,759
Bumangon ka, David!

630
00:32:44,427 --> 00:32:47,346
Keifer!

631
00:32:47,347 --> 00:32:49,432
Bumangon ka, David! bugbugin mo siya!

632
00:32:50,559 --> 00:32:51,560
bugbugin mo siya!

633
00:32:56,940 --> 00:32:58,608
suntukin mo siya!

634
00:32:59,859 --> 00:33:01,236
Go! Talunin ang kanyang asno!

635
00:33:10,537 --> 00:33:12,247
- David!
- Tayo na, Keifer!

636
00:33:21,756 --> 00:33:28,221
Keifer!

637
00:33:29,347 --> 00:33:32,100
Ang nanalo at ang class president pa rin namin!

638
00:33:32,934 --> 00:33:35,561
Mark Keifer Watson!

639
00:33:35,562 --> 00:33:38,272
[nagpapalakpak]

640
00:33:38,273 --> 00:33:44,570
Keifer!

641
00:33:44,571 --> 00:33:52,571
Keifer!

642
00:33:57,477 --> 00:33:59,797
Keifer!

643
00:34:01,004 --> 00:34:03,965
I'm so sorry, kaibigan ko.

644
00:34:06,468 --> 00:34:07,677
Hoy, David.

645
00:34:08,678 --> 00:34:09,929
Umalis ka na lang.

646
00:34:10,138 --> 00:34:11,431
- Ayos ka lang ba?
- Ayos lang ako.

647
00:34:12,557 --> 00:34:14,016
Hayaan mo na lang ako.

648
00:34:14,017 --> 00:34:15,100
ayos lang ako.

649
00:34:15,101 --> 00:34:17,771
Hindi ka okay. tignan mo.
Nasugatan ka.

650
00:34:17,979 --> 00:34:19,521
Gusto mo bang iulat ito sa paaralan?

651
00:34:19,522 --> 00:34:21,362
Ako ang nakakuha
kasali sa away diba?

652
00:34:21,566 --> 00:34:23,484
Sa tingin mo ba ay mayroon akong
lakas ng loob na sabihin sa kanila?

653
00:34:23,485 --> 00:34:24,486
Sige na.

654
00:34:25,278 --> 00:34:26,946
Hayaan mo lang akong tulungan ka.

655
00:34:27,572 --> 00:34:28,572
Gagawin ko...

656
00:34:28,615 --> 00:34:30,033
Hindi, manatili ka lang diyan.

657
00:34:33,286 --> 00:34:35,121
Huwag subukang kumilos nang cool. Dito.

658
00:34:35,747 --> 00:34:38,541
Isuot mo ito. Kaya walang tao
makikita kayong lahat na bugbog.

659
00:34:40,251 --> 00:34:41,544
Bakit mo ako tinutulungan?

660
00:34:43,296 --> 00:34:44,756
Kailangan ko ba ng dahilan para tumulong?

661
00:34:45,090 --> 00:34:46,090
Halika.

662
00:34:47,133 --> 00:34:48,677
Ayusin mo ang sarili mo.

663
00:34:57,060 --> 00:34:58,060
Halika.

664
00:34:58,853 --> 00:34:59,854
Bumangon ka na.

665
00:35:15,203 --> 00:35:18,832
Class... see you tomorrow.

666
00:35:19,082 --> 00:35:20,709
Sir, baka next year?

667
00:35:23,211 --> 00:35:25,838
- Sige. Magkita tayo sa susunod na taon.
- Paalam, ginoo.

668
00:35:25,839 --> 00:35:27,047
See you, sir!

669
00:35:27,048 --> 00:35:28,800
- Mag-ingat ka.
- Dahan-dahan, ginoo.

670
00:35:29,926 --> 00:35:31,553
- Paalam, ginoo.
- Mag-ingat ka.

671
00:35:32,011 --> 00:35:33,096
May dala ka bang pagkain?

672
00:35:33,179 --> 00:35:34,859
Syempre. Nagdala din ako ng para sa iyo.

673
00:35:34,889 --> 00:35:36,182
- Oo!
- Gusto mo bang kainin ito?

674
00:35:36,474 --> 00:35:37,474
Syempre.

675
00:35:39,144 --> 00:35:40,145
Salamat, Jay.

676
00:35:42,564 --> 00:35:43,564
Gusto ng ilan?

677
00:35:44,399 --> 00:35:44,941
Oo.

678
00:35:45,150 --> 00:35:47,902
Sa susunod, magdadala ako
para din sayo. Sa ngayon, kainin mo ito.

679
00:35:48,528 --> 00:35:49,195
Tss.

680
00:35:49,195 --> 00:35:50,071
Salamat, Jay-jay.

681
00:35:50,072 --> 00:35:51,352
- Mas maganda ba ang pakiramdam mo?
- Oo.

682
00:35:53,950 --> 00:35:54,950
Hoy, David.

683
00:35:55,076 --> 00:35:56,161
Maligayang pagbabalik.

684
00:35:56,369 --> 00:35:57,569
- Salamat, tao.
- Namiss kita.

685
00:35:57,746 --> 00:35:58,746
Tara kain na tayo.

686
00:35:59,038 --> 00:36:00,080
Kainin mo lahat, okay.

687
00:36:00,081 --> 00:36:01,582
- Gutom na gutom na ako.
- Kumain ka na rin.

688
00:36:01,583 --> 00:36:03,585
- Sige, okay lang ako.
- Salamat.

689
00:36:05,670 --> 00:36:06,670
Masarap ba?

690
00:36:06,963 --> 00:36:07,963
Mmm.

691
00:36:09,507 --> 00:36:10,592
Guys!

692
00:36:12,260 --> 00:36:14,471
Ipinadala ni Miss Assunta si a
mensahe sa panggrupong chat.

693
00:36:14,669 --> 00:36:16,546
Magkakaroon kami ng PE class sa gym.

694
00:36:17,140 --> 00:36:18,432
- Ngayon na?
- Oo.

695
00:36:18,433 --> 00:36:19,225
- Halika.
- Tara na.

696
00:36:19,226 --> 00:36:21,143
- Magpapalit lang ako ng damit.
- Dinala mo ba ang iyong uniporme?

697
00:36:21,144 --> 00:36:23,730
Umm, oo.
nakuha ko na. Magpapalit na ako.

698
00:36:26,858 --> 00:36:29,444
<i>[Nagdadaldalan ang mga mag-aaral]</i>

699
00:36:34,407 --> 00:36:36,910
Bakit lahat kayo nagbabago dito?
Hindi mo ba nakikitang may babae?

700
00:36:37,160 --> 00:36:38,745
<i>[nagtatawanan ang mga mag-aaral]</i>

701
00:36:39,204 --> 00:36:40,371
What the hell?

702
00:36:44,167 --> 00:36:46,377
Diyos ko, napakakulit mo!

703
00:37:22,580 --> 00:37:24,122
Mukhang nag-eenjoy ka.

704
00:37:24,123 --> 00:37:25,123
Magandang view?

705
00:37:25,291 --> 00:37:27,292
Diyos, hindi! Ano sa tingin mo ako, nauuhaw?

706
00:37:27,293 --> 00:37:28,293
Ang kulit nyo lahat!

707
00:37:29,170 --> 00:37:30,839
Kaya ba nakatitig ka sa...

708
00:37:31,506 --> 00:37:32,257
Isara mo ang iyong bibig.

709
00:37:32,258 --> 00:37:33,258
Magpapalit na ako.

710
00:37:35,385 --> 00:37:37,344
Ilipat! Umalis ka sa daan!

711
00:37:37,345 --> 00:37:38,345
Ilipat! Ilipat!

712
00:37:49,357 --> 00:37:50,717
Tingnan mo kung saan ka pupunta ha?

713
00:37:51,401 --> 00:37:55,362
<i>[nanunukso ng mga mag-aaral]</i>

714
00:37:55,363 --> 00:37:56,656
Busted!

715
00:37:57,115 --> 00:37:58,449
Busted!

716
00:38:03,872 --> 00:38:05,039
Halika girls, kape?

717
00:38:05,331 --> 00:38:06,790
Uy, magkita tayo mamaya, okay?

718
00:38:06,791 --> 00:38:08,209
Bye, see you.

719
00:38:08,376 --> 00:38:09,752
Magkakape tayo.

720
00:38:11,170 --> 00:38:12,170
Yo!

721
00:38:12,630 --> 00:38:13,630
Aries!

722
00:38:13,715 --> 00:38:14,715
Anong meron?

723
00:38:14,799 --> 00:38:17,468
Gusto mong makita kung anong kalokohan
